        <mxCell id="7OVz4w7n9kzEPWy-4BBC-9" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#007CBD;strokeColor=none;fontColor=#FFFFFF;fontStyle=1;fontSize=22;labelBackgroundColor=none;" value="6" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="38" width="40" x="1170" y="492" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7OVz4w7n9kzEPWy-4BBC-10" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#007CBD;strokeColor=none;fontColor=#FFFFFF;fontStyle=1;fontSize=22;labelBackgroundColor=none;" value="7" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="38" width="40" x="1169.5" y="577" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7OVz4w7n9kzEPWy-4BBC-13" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=-4;fontSize=14;labelBackgroundColor=none;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Secure Network Transit:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1&quot;&gt; AWS Site-to-Site VPN establishes an encrypted IPsec tunnel connecting the on-premises infrastructure to the AWS Asia Pacific (Jakarta) Region, ensuring secure data migration and administration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="77.5" width="449" x="1220.5" y="62.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7OVz4w7n9kzEPWy-4BBC-14" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=-4;fontSize=14;labelBackgroundColor=none;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Automated Database Migration:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1&quot;&gt;AWS Database Migration Service (DMS), utilized alongside the AWS Schema Conversion Tool (SCT), extracts the legacy on-premises databases and establishes a continuous Change Data Capture (CDC) pipeline.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2&quot;&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90.5" width="450" x="1219.5" y="139.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7OVz4w7n9kzEPWy-4BBC-15" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=-4;fontSize=14;labelBackgroundColor=none;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Edge Traffic Routing:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1&quot;&gt;Amazon Route 53 provides highly available Domain Name System (DNS) resolution, reliably routing external customer requests into the cloud environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="117" width="450" x="1219.5" y="238.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7OVz4w7n9kzEPWy-4BBC-16" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=-4;fontSize=14;labelBackgroundColor=none;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Near-Zero Downtime Synchronization:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1&quot;&gt;The continuous data stream securely ingests into the cloud database, maintaining strict data integrity and a near-zero Recovery Point Objective (RPO) during the migration cutover window.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;7,2&quot;&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;9&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="121" width="450" x="1219.5" y="316.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7OVz4w7n9kzEPWy-4BBC-17" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=-4;fontSize=14;labelBackgroundColor=none;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;8,1&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Elastic Load Distribution:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;8,1&quot;&gt;The Application Load Balancer (ALB) receives inbound traffic and intelligently distributes HTTP/HTTPS requests across the Amazon EC2 Auto Scaling Group to ensure optimal performance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="114" width="449" x="1220.5" y="401.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7OVz4w7n9kzEPWy-4BBC-18" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=-4;fontSize=14;labelBackgroundColor=none;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;b&gt;Modernized Persistence Layer:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;The compute tier interacts with Amazon Aurora PostgreSQL. It is deployed in a Multi-Availability Zone topology to guarantee enterprise-grade high availability and automated failover.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="118" width="450" x="1220.5" y="493.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="7OVz4w7n9kzEPWy-4BBC-19" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=-4;fontSize=14;labelBackgroundColor=none;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;10,1&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Scalable Analytics Storage:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;10,1&quot;&gt;Application servers seamlessly load raw and cleansed analytics data into Amazon S3, leveraging its robust 99.999999999% durability to permanently replace fragile physical storage.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;10,2&quot;&gt;&lt;sup class=&quot;superscript&quot; data-turn-source-index=&quot;9&quot;&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="113" width="449" x="1220.5" y="577.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
